nodes.text: CL-33/890 was a clone trooper 2nd Lieutenant in the Grand Army of the Republic during the Clone Wars. He worked with Four-One, CT-6/774, and CT-014/783 on a LAAT/i gunship during the Battle of Haruun Kal, operating the navigation system. His gunship was assigned to the medium cruiser Halleck.
His gunship sustained heavy damage during the space battle at Haruun Kal, though the ship endured and assisted with the post-battle rescue of stranded clones.
